{"tid":15951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真心唔明點解仲要理個班on9低質打手","createTime":"2016-12-01T08:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T17:54:41.000Z","uid":26249,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd84682980e7bad92f7fbb0405567502eed9ed99","tid":15951,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"其實直接block左佢然後無視咪得<br />\n點解咁認真同佢地癲<br />\n佢地開post明引你地鬧尻佢架啦<br />\n你一屌佢地 佢地咪有位繼續入繼續推post囉<br />\n班打手見咁好反應做唔拿拿聲開多幾個ac 瘋狂開post洗版咩？<br />\n唔好比反應佢地 由佢地自己單機咪算啦<br />\n仲要認真討論都唔知咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你方你屌完佢佢就會收手咩<br />\n屌完佢地你會開心啲咩<br />\n搞班成個forum都充斥住呢啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地自言自語一排都會變得冇咁積極架啦<br />\n你地係都要同佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等佢地開post開得咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重申一次 邊個幫打手推post 就同打手冇分別"},{"pid":"b83f78f6fc1ea99f9d4ee64362f1c71113e3c413","tid":15951,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:42:29.000Z","msg":"樓主又搞分化<br />\n死返高登啦你"},{"pid":"be75be39b99dd150ee63cbbde37b255e72bb9a7f","tid":15951,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主又搞分化<br />\n死返高登啦你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1dfd9bc5cd2a9ffca442cc15daec8a44d4e9b4","tid":15951,"uid":3488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"打手post推到上熱門真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d85b152ae838902a4e0ff12a4841be73f82d62","tid":15951,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打手post推到上熱門真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要唔只一個post上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6513d26f0f846a03e0c155dea47a7c46b0eb55f6","tid":15951,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"要推，幾個打手ACCOUNT就成事，高登時事台就係咁俾熱狗五毛霸哂，完全唔俾機會人地討論。變左黎來黎去都係個五六個ACCOUNT 推POST&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然，最重係高登垃圾ADMIN縱容班打手先會攪成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa5990dcddf8fe163d2ca64ef79a79c8a64dd1f","tid":15951,"uid":34880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位巴絲見到打手post入去block咗佢就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔需要留言/負皮 <br />\n由得d仆街單機就會自摺㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n係 睇到打手寫d嘢係會燥燥地 <br />\n但諗深一層 回post = 加佢人工<br />\n理撚得佢班撚樣講乜都唔好回<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c44ac83a0754be8b4f4d49c7c1e7d97b9dac90e","tid":15951,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位巴絲見到打手post入去block咗佢就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔需要留言/負皮 <br />\n由得d仆街單機就會自摺㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n係 睇到打手寫d嘢係會燥燥地 <br />\n但諗深一層 回post = 加佢人工<br />\n理撚得佢班撚樣講乜都唔好回<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 